t: "And ЋєrememberЋЇ when Abraham said, вАЬMy Lord, make this city Ћєof MeccaЋЇ secure and provide fruits to its peopleвАФthose among them who believe in Allah and the Last Day.вАЭ He answered, вАЬAs for those who disbelieve, I will let them enjoy themselves for a little while, then I will condemn them to the torment of the Fire. What an evil destination!вАЭ"